SUMMARY:Community Block Party for History
DESCRIPTION:The Stevens & Smith Center Grand Opening takes over East Vine Street for a buzzing community block party on Saturday\, May 2 from 12-6pm! Local artists\, musicians\, and neighbors bring the streets to life with creativity\, energy\, and good vibes. Families and friends can dive into hands-on activities and enjoy free timed entry to explore the Center.\n\nFree & open to the public. All are welcome!\n\nA more detailed schedule of programming\, vendors\, and tickets to visit the Stevens & Smith Center will be released in mid-April.
URL:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/event/block-party/
LOCATION:The Stevens & Smith Center\, 13-15 East Vine Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/BlockParty_Web.png
END:VEVENT
